% rottxt function came from https://stackoverflow.com/questions/12599627/how-can-i-write-arc-text-in-postscript-file
/rottxt { 4 dict begin
    /ang exch def
    /str exch def
    /ang ang str length div def
    { pop pop ang rotate }
    str
    kshow
end } def
%face
6 inch 7 inch moveto
/Palatino-Roman 18 selectfont
(This is a smile! This is a smile! This is a smile! This is a smile! This is a smile! This is a smile!) 360 rottxt

%mouth
